-url-token" content="21542890"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="116365839"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="474626014"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/21542890/answer/474626014">宜家的家具是否质量很差，理由是什么？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>11</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">11</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/wang-tong-77-64" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-tong-77-64'>王通</a>，<span title="集祥家居 品牌联合创始人暨首席设计师" class="bio">集祥家居 品牌联合创始人暨首席设计师</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="王通" data-entry-url="/question/21542890/answer/474626014"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">网上关于宜家的产品质量一直是个很热门的话题，每次宜家出现品质问题都会有大批的媒体关注，比如前一段时间天价的“夺命抽屉柜”赔偿案，久而久之好像形成了以宜家=低品质这样一种主观印象。 实际上我们评价一个品牌或企业的产品应该站在他的定位和价格区间…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/21542890/answer/474626014">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="11"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/lisong-3" data-hovercard='p$t$lisong-3'>SStargazer</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/liu-bo-qiang-13" data-hovercard='p$t$liu-bo-qiang-13'>梦回大唐</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/xiang-gu-xiao-xiao-ni" data-hovercard='p$t$xiang-gu-xiao-xiao-ni'>香菇小小呢</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content">网上关于宜家的产品质量一直是个很热门的话题，每次宜家出现品质问题都会有大批的媒体关注，比如前一段时间天价的“夺命抽屉柜”赔偿案，久而久之好像形成了以宜家=低品质这样一种主观印象。<br>       实际上我们评价一个品牌或企业的产品应该站在他的定位和价格区间来判断，宜家的定位是让大多数人尤其是年轻人都能用的起的，环保的，经过用心设计的家居，从这一点上来说，宜家无疑是成功的，如果让高端家具的消费者来站在他们的立场上来评判宜家是不公平的。<br>        宜家的品质把控，模式，标准化和成本控制都是基础性家具定位的标杆，事实上如果花费宜家同样的预算来采购国内很多三无山寨工厂的产品，有可能连板材最基础的环保指标都做不到，更别提其他的设计体验之类的了。所以如果你是准备用宜家的预算来采购家具，那么宜家无疑是最好的选择。<br>    当然，宜家也有自己的问题，宜家在国内的很多产品跟国外还是有差距的，包括售后政策等，这也是宜家饱受诟病的一个点。  <br><br><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3b21b56ebbdea961e8b6cdf75ab988fd_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="558" data-rawheight="312" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="558" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3b21b56ebbdea961e8b6cdf75ab988fd_r.jpg"></figure>宜家是一个较低造价的，相对品质可控的家居选择方案。</script><a class="time" href="/question/21542890/answer/474626014">2018-08-21</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>11</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="797898"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">4 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b145d37035554ec1b70863618e7bb129_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button class="button-text"><i class="sprite-global-icon-fold-round-default"></i>收起</button></li><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop phone-actions"><button class="button-text menubutton"><i class="fi fi-3-dot"></i>更多</button><div class="menu goog-menu goog-menu-vertical zh-answer-more-actions" style="display:none"><div class="goog-menuitem js-share">分享</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-collect">收藏</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-thank ">感谢</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-report">举报</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b145d37035554ec1b70863618e7bb129_m.jpg"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></div></div></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-116368821"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/264863189/answer/474642432"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="20376445"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="264863189"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="116368821"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="474642432"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/264863189/answer/474642432">实木家具、实木多层板家具的区别是什么？他们大概的价格区间又是多少呢？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>2</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">2</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/wang-tong-77-64" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-tong-77-64'>王通</a>，<span title="集祥家居 品牌联合创始人暨首席设计师" class="bio">集祥家居 品牌联合创始人暨首席设计师</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="王通" data-entry-url="/question/264863189/answer/474642432"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">实木的家具耐用，可做的造型丰富，样式多样，各种木材有各自的质感美，缺点是造价高，使用过程中需要有保养意识，使用不当有开裂变形的风险。 板材的家具制作方便，对资源的利用率高，造价低，好的板材家具品质也很高，比如欧洲现代家具其实大部分是板式的…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/264863189/answer/474642432">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="2"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/lisong-3" data-hovercard='p$t$lisong-3'>SStargazer</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/san-ye-61-58" data-hovercard='p$t$san-ye-61-58'>叁叶</a></span></span> <span>赞同</span></div><script type="text" class="content">       实木的家具耐用，可做的造型丰富，样式多样，各种木材有各自的质感美，缺点是造价高，使用过程中需要有保养意识，使用不当有开裂变形的风险。<br>       板材的家具制作方便，对资源的利用率高，造价低，好的板材家具品质也很高，比如欧洲现代家具其实大部分是板式的。<br>       在国内市场板材家具比较混杂，存在相当比例环保不达标的板式家具，因此尽可能选择品牌口碑较好的产品。整体上来说，现代家庭选择板木结合的家居比较现实合理。<br><br><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-842e4c42a590f53fe4e63165de83aa20_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="546" data-rawheight="410" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="546" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-842e4c42a590f53fe4e63165de83aa20_r.jpg"></figure>实木有很好的形体可塑性，板式则有稳定性高，节约资源的优点，未来板木结合家具应该会成为市场的主流，没有必要特别要求“全实木”，有些柜体部分用全实木做反而是不合理的。<br><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3179a0fa107f87c359ef8dbc1e5a9c0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="558" data-rawheight="391" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="558" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3179a0fa107f87c359ef8dbc1e5a9c0_r.jpg"></figure>意大利品牌ceccotti的产品，典型的板木结合做法，充分结合了实木和板式两者的优点。</script><a class="time" href="/question/264863189/answer/474642432">2018-08-21</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>2</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="20376445"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">添加评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b145d37035554ec1b70863618e7bb129_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button class="button-text"><i class="sprite-global-icon-fold-round-default"></i>收起</button></li><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop phone-actions"><button class="button-text menubutton"><i class="fi fi-3-dot"></i>更多</button><div class="menu goog-menu goog-menu-vertical zh-answer-more-actions" style="display:none"><div class="goog-menuitem js-share">分享</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-collect">收藏</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-thank ">感谢</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-report">举报